{
  "stem": "15082.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 398.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no forced work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I chose to go to work in the warehouse that was distributing the food to the people in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my dad worked in there too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We both went to work daily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was just unloading trucks of food that were brought in, opening up the cartons, and shelving it out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then people would come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the kitchen facilities was available.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if you didn't want to, you just got your rationing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could take it back to your living quarters, and get your portions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a kosher kitchen and an un-kosher kitchen in Foehrenwald.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember the first time, which I had never seen because in our part of the world, there was very little cannery stuff.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything was fresh, living in these small towns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't realize what a can of spam meant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I read it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It looked good then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But-- and it was-- a lot of the rationing stuff that they got was because of what was left over from the army stuff that they did not use.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was just loads and loads of stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they kept bringing it in every day through the operations of UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the joint distribution was very heavily involved in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one of them that was outstanding in my mind was-- that I have seen, the mayor of New York, Fiorello La Guardia, that came to camp to see, you know, how we're living, which he was concerned.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think at that time, he maybe even represented the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was his mission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's why he was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, you know, when I read Fiorello La Guardia was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
